      "content": "it's just so exhausting. everyone keeps talking about \"moving on\" or \"starting over,\" but it feels like they're asking a ghost to go back to work. the version of me that people loved is dead, so i feel like i might as well follow. if that person is gone, what's left for me to actually live for?",
